name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: AutoBrowser - Automate your browser with AI

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
AutoBrowser puts the power of AI in your browser so that you can automate tasks simply by describing it. Powered by Claude 3.5 Computer Use.

Disclaimer: AutoBrowser is an educational product meant for experimenting with the latest developments in AI. It often makes mistakes in executing tasks and should not be used for real-world use cases. Please exercise caution and supervise AI actions at all times during operation.
